    "# Rope Flow \u2014 Full Pipeline V02\n## Data-Driven Pattern Classification\n\n**Course:** MECH 798M / EECE 798K \u2014 Data-Driven Modeling  \n**Input:** Processed CSV files (Device 0 + Device 1)  \n**Output:** Per-cycle + session-level pattern classification\n\n### Pipeline architecture (56D feature vector per cycle)\n\n| # | Stage | Dim | DDM method |\n|---|-------|-----|-----------|\n| 1 | Cycle detection | \u2014 | Signal processing: ||\u03c9|| peaks |\n| 2 | Physics features | 12D | Pillar 6: period, symmetry, phase lag, jerk, energy |\n| 3 | Fourier decomposition | 16D | Pillar 5: dominant freq, harmonics, spectral entropy |\n| 4 | SVD features | 8D | Pillar 4: singular value ratios, effective rank |\n| 5 | Template correlation | 2D | Phase-aligned similarity to class template |\n| 6 | DMD eigenvalues | 9D | Pillar 4: dynamical fingerprint per cycle |\n| 7 | Subject-invariant | 9D | Pillar 6: D1/D0 ratios, skewness, kurtosis |"
   ]
  },
